<lb ed="L" n="0267b03"/>也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>臆</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0267b0303" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">伊力切音億<term rend="no_nor">胷</term>臆</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>攖</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0267b0311" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">伊盈切音纓觸也迫近也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>駁</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL154p0267b0322" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">比用切音博與
<lb ed="L" n="0267b04"/>駮同論列是非謂之駮</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
